<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>package_private</access><active>true</active><api_name>x_1394653_gxt.gatherNumber</api_name><caller_access/><client_callable>true</client_callable><description/><name>gatherNumber</name><script><![CDATA[var gatherNumber = Class.create();
gatherNumber.prototype = Object.extendsObject(global.AbstractAjaxProcessor, {

	numberDetail: function() {

		var number = '';
		var userid = this.getParamter('sysparm_user_sysid');

		var gr = new GlideRecord('sys_user');
		gr.addQuery('sys_id', userid);
		gr.query();

		if (gr.next()) {
			number = gr.getValue('number');
		}

		return number;
	},
    type: 'gatherNumber'
});]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2024-08-21 18:25:50</sys_created_on><sys_id>ba3157d3834412106d3e5e20ceaad3cd</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>gatherNumber</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Galactic Experiment Tracker" source="x_1394653_gxt">c21be6d3838012106d3e5e20ceaad388</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Galactic Experiment Tracker">c21be6d3838012106d3e5e20ceaad388</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_ba3157d3834412106d3e5e20ceaad3cd</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2024-08-21 18:25:50</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>
